site_name: Millbrook Park (Former Inglis Barracks)Mill Hill EastNW7
description: Full Planning Permission for Phase 6B, associated with the Millbrook Park development, for the erection of 2 linked buildings 6 storeys in height comprising 82 residential units (Use Class C3), 615sqm (GIA) of employment space (Use Class B1), together with associated plant, car parking, cycle parking, refuse stores, servicing areas and associated hard and soft landscaping
